Package: financr
Title:  Retrieve Financial Data From Yahoo Finance
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R:
    person("ClÃ©ment", "Laverdet", , "clementlvd@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", 'cph'),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4466-3394"))
Description: Retrieve historical market data (e.g., market prices, currencies exchange rates) ; 
     latest insights on  financial assets, major indices, currencies and crypto-currencies ;
     and various helper functions, e.g., retrieves the latest exchange rates, find symbol validity or similar assets.
